<br>
My 2nd level Dark Elf SK using a rusty broadsword consistently gets more than 12. He hits less often and of course doesn't crit,  but ??? Why isn't the master doing better with damage? I thought there was a damage cap that lifted after 20? I haven't seen adifference.<br>
<br>
Anyone offer any help?<br>
<br>
BTW - I'm broke, so purchasing new weapons isn't likely in the near future.<br>
<br>
I'm currently at the Lake of Ill Omen.<br>
